[12:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'assistant\'s going to investigate, come up with a hypothesis on what it thinks the root cause of this issue is. It\'s going to add debug logging to the project to establish for sure whether or'

[12:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'not its hypothesis is correct or incorrect and then it\'s going to start the server. And then it hands back to me to reproduce the issue. So, I\'ll interact with the voice AI and reproduce'

[13:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the issue. And then I\'ll hand back to the assistant and it\'s going to check logs and determine whether or not its hypothesis was correct. If it is, it\'s going to reset the code base using Git'

[13:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and add a fix. And then it hands back to me to do the testing. And I\'ll check whether or not it\'s correct. And that\'s an actual fix. And if it is, we'

[13:30] [scene:talk]
